Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.65,0:00:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.73,0:00:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翌晨的陽光就快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.83,0:00:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照進這間充滿煙蒂\N雜亂無章的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.71,0:00:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why 聖母瑪利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.81,0:00:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對溫柔感到飢渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.95,0:00:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.75,0:00:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼孤單的夜晚\N總是如此漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.70,0:00:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛仔褲下的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.50,0:00:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被破碎的夢想打溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.87,0:01:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著襯衫的胸部太過耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.84,0:01:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.65,0:01:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.22,0:01:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是幻覺也太鮮明了點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.16,0:01:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代明明不可能\N出現在這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.07,0:02:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒修好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.07,0:02:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.57,0:02:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要追上觀光巴士就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.14,0:02:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道巴士的路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.18,0:02:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們已經抄近路\N走在他們前面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看,沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.32,0:02:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.67,0:02:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上就住在這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,妳看妳看,好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.74,0:02:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太太,太太\N聽說這一帶有很多很棒的溫泉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.58,0:02:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回程真想去泡一泡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.88,0:02:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皮膚會變得水水嫩嫩的唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,不來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.25,0:02:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泡溫泉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.42,0:02:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#62 太好了!和響子泡男女混浴\N露天溫泉兩人獨處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在這裡,真是怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發的時間到了,請快上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都上車了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.27,0:03:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.87,0:03:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,那位小姐啊\N她在前一站下車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.94,0:03:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.04,0:03:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然說要去泡溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.04,0:03:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有說要去哪個溫泉嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.45,0:03:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得她好像是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.20,0:04:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到是到了,但不曉得是哪家旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.24,0:04:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,既然這樣\N就一家家的地毯式搜尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是從東京來的啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.72,0:04:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,本來預定要去輪島的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.09,0:04:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然改變行程來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連旅館都還沒訂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.76,0:04:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊\N那我幫妳介紹我朋友的旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.70,0:04:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無響子小姐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.37,0:04:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裡沒有這位客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.91,0:04:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.42,0:05:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.26,0:05:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好,我是剛才打電話來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.07,0:05:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,有有,我有接到電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.71,0:05:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.95,0:05:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臨時改變主意來這裡\N真是來對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.69,0:05:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.43,0:05:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,一之瀨太太嗎?\N我是音無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.06,0:05:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我臨時改變了行程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.66,0:05:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想把旅館的電話號碼\N跟妳說一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.50,0:05:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看妳又來了,不要緊啦\N這裡一切都很平安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.84,0:06:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,還是留個電話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.11,0:06:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.71,0:06:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,對了,現在水電工來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.15,0:06:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在做定期檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.55,0:06:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗臉台下面的水管生鏽了\N他現在正在換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.65,0:06:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.22,0:06:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會隨便處理好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.49,0:06:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.39,0:06:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦\N少妳一個人不會怎樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有,大家都好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.23,0:06:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好,都很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很好,要帶土產回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.68,0:06:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣囉\N五代和大家都很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.85,0:06:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來\N這兩三天都沒看到五代耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.59,0:06:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代果然在東京啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.18,0:07:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不在這個小鎮嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.02,0:07:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之先找個地方落腳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.72,0:07:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,你是從東京來的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.26,0:07:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.40,0:07:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐,妳泡過露天溫泉了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,有露天溫泉嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.71,0:07:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊,來到這裡\N一定要泡露天溫泉才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.55,0:07:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男生和女生有分開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.72,0:07:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上人很少,泡起來很舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是沒辦法追到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.33,0:08:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想在觀光勝地的人群裡找人\N看來是不可能的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.50,0:08:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天她就要回東京了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.24,0:08:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明天也得回東京去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.95,0:08:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是打工\N也不能老是請假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.79,0:08:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員現在在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管躺著坐著都好無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.24,0:08:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去泡一下露天溫泉好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.81,0:08:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(大露天浴池)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.61,0:09:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,裡面幾乎連在一起嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.71,0:09:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.55,0:09:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.35,0:09:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正又沒有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.27,0:09:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要回東京了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.51,0:10:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼老是看到五代的幻影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.75,0:10:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道我其實很期待\N他追來這裡找我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.32,0:10:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在你身邊\N你也不要緊是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她為什麼要哭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.98,0:11:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,我開始頭暈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.16,0:11:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊,原來有別人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有別人在這裡啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.10,0:11:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五…五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.51,0:12:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那個…\N-那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.71,0:12:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?\N難道他是來找我的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.78,0:12:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是夢吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.02,0:12:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追上了,我終於追上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.13,0:12:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你是來旅行的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.44,0:12:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有浮上來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.56,0:13:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五…五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.06,0:13:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快來人啊!來人啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的\N他只是泡暈了頭而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.35,0:13:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.57,0:13:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?\N竟然抬到我的房裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他會在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是來找我的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.20,0:14:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我對妳已經沒有感覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.07,0:14:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是,只是單純的巧合?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你怎麼會在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.72,0:14:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來找妳的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.22,0:14:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來找妳的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來…是夢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.40,0:14:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是\N怎麼可能那麼湊巧碰到管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.54,0:14:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.08,0:15:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有覺得好一點了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.59,0:15:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得你在露天溫泉昏倒了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.59,0:15:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.04,0:15:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉\N給妳添了很多麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.58,0:15:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.71,0:15:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我泡茶給你喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.77,0:15:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那個…\N-那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.47,0:16:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是來旅行的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.84,0:16:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,臨時決定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.88,0:16:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好巧喔\N居然來同一個地方旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.71,0:16:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,我還嚇了一大跳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.79,0:16:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很巧,居然連旅館都同一間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.82,0:16:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間可以看到海\N真的很漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.89,0:16:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的房間也可以看得到海喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.90,0:16:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是巧合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.44,0:16:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來找妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.78,0:16:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟三鷹後來怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.05,0:16:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候,妳為什麼要哭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.96,0:16:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然很想問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-請問…\N-什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.80,0:17:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有,我是想問\N可以喝啤酒嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.43,0:17:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在喝啤酒不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝點涼的比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.08,0:17:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也來喝一點好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.59,0:17:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.31,0:17:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.27,0:17:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想問你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想問你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.75,0:17:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.62,0:17:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還在誤會我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.79,0:17:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.75,0:17:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去三鷹家探病時發生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.66,0:17:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.46,0:18:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不在意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.06,0:18:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不喜歡被人誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.62,0:19:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原…原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.85,0:19:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.76,0:19:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.92,0:19:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個大豬頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.03,0:19:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說…那時候的眼淚是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.74,0:19:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我說了那種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.35,0:19:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我沒有注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.92,0:19:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.13,0:19:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒真好喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.07,0:19:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.71,0:20:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇見五代之後,覺得輕鬆多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.12,0:20:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,真的是巧合嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.43,0:20:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定其實他是來找我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.30,0:20:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是這樣,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.01,0:20:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會是誰啊?都這麼晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.25,0:20:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,管理員,是我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.82,0:20:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我有問妳旅館的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.56,0:20:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳聽得到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.66,0:20:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水管又爆掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.43,0:20:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水管?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.86,0:21:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好享受你的旅行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.87,0:21:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.61,0:21:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問,這個房間的小姐呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.24,0:21:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,那位小姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.74,0:21:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在天亮前就出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.31,0:21:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說要搭第一班電車回東京去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.82,0:21:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.55,0:21:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.60,0:21:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好慘喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.76,0:22:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.50,0:22:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在走廊上幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.97,0:22:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了慶祝水管修復\N我們正想喝一杯慶祝一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.41,0:22:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.91,0:22:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代沒有去找妳嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.34,0:22:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追去金澤?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.25,0:22:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的,剛才大家一直在聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.72,0:22:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從妳去旅行的那天晚上\N五代就沒回來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.49,0:22:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且妳不是把旅行日程表\N貼在妳的門上嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.72,0:22:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.79,0:22:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想\N從那天晚上就不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.86,0:22:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,應該說被拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.57,0:22:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後啊,為了慎重起見\N我打電話去幼稚園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.34,0:22:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們說前天\N五代從金澤打電話來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.24,0:22:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說他去旅行了,要請假幾天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.14,0:22:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前天不就是\N妳去金澤的第二天嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.21,0:22:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.62,0:22:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,五代果然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.62,0:23:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N我不知道五代的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.26,0:23:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.03,0:23:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,得來個大掃除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.70,0:23:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你們也要來幫忙喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.77,0:23:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪了\N突然變得那麼有幹勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.00,0:23:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是五代\N到底跑到哪裡去了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.84,0:23:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這真是個謎團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.18,0:23:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在說我的壞話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.41,0:23:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是因為我睡著了\N她一氣之下跑回去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.20,0:23:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?\N五代當八神的家教老師?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.74,0:23:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊\N他被那個女孩搞得團團轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.35,0:23:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕美眉\N如果豁了出去,可是很恐怖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.65,0:23:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.35,0:24:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『馬力全開的八神\N在遺忘的時刻到來!』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.99,0:24:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,振作一點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.20,0:24:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人坐在黎明的護欄上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.72,0:24:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今一直在尋找遺落愛的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.43,0:24:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.64,0:24:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…一陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.01,0:25:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目光交會…只有…再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.18,0:25:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.28,0:25:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…在雨中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.65,0:25:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忽然…胸口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.09,0:25:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢…濡濕而發光
